{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idab6660a9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9132"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9132"},"text":"§ 9132.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regular Air Force and Space Force: gender-free basis for acceptance of original enlistments","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In accepting persons for original enlistment in the Regular Air Force or the Space Force, the Secretary of the Air Force may not—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idab6660aa-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9132/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" set a minimum or maximum percentage of persons who may be accepted for such an enlistment according to gender for skill categories or jobs; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idab6660ab-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9132/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" in any other way base the acceptance of a person for such an enlistment on gender.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idab6660ac-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/456/dA/tV/s522/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–456, div. A, title V, § 522(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-09-29"},"text":"Sept. 29, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/1973"},"text":"102 Stat. 1973","children":[],"tail":", § 8252; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/484/dA/tX/s1052/40"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–484, div. A, title X, § 1052(40)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date",